snippet.title: Bionic Commando: Rearmed Intro & Theme
snippet.description:
It's the enhanced remake of the fantabulastic NES game. It has gameplay, controls and graphics true to the original. It has new characters, runs on PhysX and includes great chiptune music. What's not to like?

This was a HD screentest for my computer's FRAPS setup. IIRC, 1080p, 40-60 FPS with an overclocked OEM budget GPU included with the computer (ATI Radeon HD4350)

Music: Bionic Commando: Rearmed theme



(I did not create the music nor the game shown in this video. Capcom, GRIN and all others who made the original game deserve the credit. I simply captured it in FRAPS and uploaded it.) (C) Aidan Bayer/arbayer2. All rights reserved. All credit goes to its respective holders.
